591
00:37:59,277 --> 00:38:00,712
Come.

592
00:38:00,737 --> 00:38:02,298
What, what, what?

593
00:38:02,322 --> 00:38:04,258
Let's go, darling.

594
00:38:04,282 --> 00:38:08,386
Come.

595
00:38:08,411 --> 00:38:11,389
Yes, yes, yes.

596
